## Amazon application ##
Three portals in amazon application:
   1) Admin  2) Merchant  3) User
   
** Admin Portal **
Admin name     = Gokul
Admin password = 1234

[ Admin can approve merchant , add merchant , view all products , remove merchant ]

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

** Merchant Portal **
Merchant name  = Ram
Password       = 5678
Merchant ID    = 100

[ Merchant can add product , remove product , View their products , sales report , stock update ]
[ You have craete a new merchant account which needs approve from admin ]

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

** User Portal **
[ There is no default user has been set. We can create a user by clicking create an account in user portal ]
[ User can view , search products , buy them , add product to cart , view their history of products ]

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
